{"tid":1884544,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[造數大國] 為左復航復工 感染人數一步步下降 治愈人數幾何級上升","createTime":"2020-02-17T15:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T10:50:43.000Z","uid":51620,"like":70,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"87e6fbc1acff62291429d9f5aca1f6c5256fd73b","tid":1884544,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5J6rSpv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5J6rSpv.jpg&h=68fc77d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8uKJabb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8uKJabb.jpg&h=c18212f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總攻，捷報！湖北首地清零</span></span></strong><br />\n今天（17日）下午，神農架林區發布一個好消息，當地率先在湖北省實現&ldquo;清零&rdquo;！<br />\n<br />\n疫情發生以來，神農架林區累計報告10例確診病例，後陸續有8人治愈。今天上午8時，最後2位患者出院。<br />\n<br />\n至此，神農架林區10例確診病例全部治愈，實現醫務人員零感染，完成確診病例治愈&ldquo;清零&rdquo;目標。截至2月16日，林區已經連續13天無新增確診病例。<br />\n<br />\n昨日，湖北省委書記、省新冠肺炎疫情防控指揮部指揮長應勇主持召開疫情防控視頻調度會。<br />\n<br />\n長安街知事注意到，這是應勇到任湖北以來，首次以省新冠肺炎疫情防控指揮部指揮長身份亮相。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.cn/gn/2020-02-17/detail-iimxyqvz3599768.d.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.cn%2Fgn%2F2020-02-17%2Fdetail-iimxyqvz3599768.d.html&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=13064b2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.cn/gn/2020-02-17/detail-iimxyqvz3599768.d.html</a>"},{"pid":"b31775989fb56694e60fbe502101be249d9e80a2","tid":1884544,"uid":3860,"like":168,"dislike":1,"score":167,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:01:21.000Z","msg":"最驚佢唔復工<br />\n見佢到封晒城都驚傳慢左<br />\n<br />\n有曱大大出手真係放心晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3fa72a3ced1427bf7d7e61e6129122ebe6e3d95","tid":1884544,"uid":51620,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"b31775989fb56694e60fbe502101be249d9e80a2","tid":1884544,"uid":3860,"like":168,"dislike":1,"score":167,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:01:21.000Z","msg":"最驚佢唔復工<br />\n見佢到封晒城都驚傳慢左<br />\n<br />\n有曱大大出手真係放心晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />前排先咁串話唔洗人幫 <br />\n佢唔復工 冇錢 一間間廠執<br />\n美帝又迫佢找數 叫佢點頂"},{"pid":"02c74d1a385e279ee984d92366d08825764d6bf9","tid":1884544,"uid":92188,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:02:57.000Z","msg":"全部清零唔難啦，聽日都可以實現<br />\n唔好出嚟咪得囉"},{"pid":"afa223d9bb3e5ee35e8a53b50ed5e2f1587693ba","tid":1884544,"uid":51620,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"02c74d1a385e279ee984d92366d08825764d6bf9","tid":1884544,"uid":92188,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:02:57.000Z","msg":"全部清零唔難啦，聽日都可以實現<br />\n唔好出嚟咪得囉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />WTO都話佢叻另豬 疫情開始轉好"},{"pid":"16fd1fc67422d64d6af14f98fa01ea74512a8e33","tid":1884544,"uid":2054,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"復工然後再爆過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56bcec53a44869801e9f47a3bb7adb6da0aad9d2","tid":1884544,"uid":72228,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"16fd1fc67422d64d6af14f98fa01ea74512a8e33","tid":188454